subSubSection.paragraph:
Post-mounting specimens
Slide-mounted adult female (n = 3): body oval to round (
Figs 1
; 
2A
), 1.9 ± 0.3 [1.6] (1.5-2.1) mm long and 1.5 ± 0.2 [1.3] (1.3-1.7) mm wide.

subSection.paragraph:
Anal ring.
105.3 ± 3.1 [108] (101-108) µm in transverse diameter, with 6 flagellate setae each 62.5 ± 7.9 (50-73) µm long with a rounded tip, and two or three inner rows of cells (
Figs 1G
; 
2C
).

